'Sithric and his guards must have given me a sleeping draught....'
'It appears that I am further in your debt, [placeholder]!'
'Sithric and his guards must have given me a sleeping draught....'
'He could not bear that we were being productive again!'
'Before I throw him in the stocks, I want to know why... why is he here?'
'It is time to take back Stangard and win the hearts of my men. Will you join me?'
'Why has he gone to such lengths to cripple us completely?'
'I am weak, but I hope you will help me....'
